findings.title: OCTD - Owner Contract Tokens Drain
findings.description: The contract owner has the authority to claim all the balance of the contract by calling the claimStuckTokens function and setting the zero address as an argument.

findings.title: ELFM - Exceed Limit Fees Manipulation
findings.description: The contract owner has the authority to increase over the allowed limit of 25%. The owner may take advantage of it by calling the setBuyFee function with high percentage values.

findings.title: ULTW - Unlimited Liquidity to Team Wallet
findings.description: The contract owner has the authority to transfer funds without limit to the team wallet. These funds have been swiped from the swap & liquify feature.
